g.title: j1494176179
g.text: I know your past is a touchy subject, but...

g.title: j2975784276
g.text: That skana of yours, I'm really curious about it.

g.title: j2802775728
g.text: Well, I could call you *Petersham* if you prefer.

g.title: j3957028884
g.text: I'm still really curious about that skana.

g.title: j2094977018
g.text: The red bandana that's tied to the blade. Whose was it?

g.title: j2396214046
g.text: Okay, now I know you're pulling my leg.

g.title: j2106729432
g.text: Nobodies. It's my favourite colour, remember?

g.title: j539868702
g.text: Courtesy of Doctor E. Ran me straight through.

g.title: j2513396014
g.text: I get to be dramatic when I earned the sword by getting stabbed with it.

g.title: j91243760
g.text: Why do I get the feeling that's not the truth?

g.title: j2590615679
g.text: You have a very odd way of letting a man know you find him attractive.

g.title: j1460346746
g.text: I had stronger words for it at the time.

g.title: j2891822274
g.text: You aren't exactly the easiest person to approach, Arthur.

g.title: j599825220
g.text: I don't have a lot of practice at this.

g.title: j4254942455
g.text: I get it. You're trying to make friends. Get to know me.

g.title: j2407795981
g.text: So I'm trying to break through the ice any way I can.

g.title: j2915358496
g.text: And I'm not making it easy on you.

g.title: j1651429582
g.text: There are some cans of worms I'm not bloody willing to open for you yet.

g.title: j2812985921
g.text: I know, I know. And you've already tried.

g.title: j2013044495
g.text: I... well, if you're serious, now's not the right time, but...

g.title: j1119986056
g.text: Bless your stubborn heart for consistency, I suppose.

g.title: j1462151428
g.text: The red bandana tied on it. Who did it belong to?

g.title: j3173934999
g.text: Sheesh, didn't realize you'd make such a big deal out of this.

g.title: j4275066340
g.text: But be honest, am I doomed here?

g.title: j1921425661
g.text: No grudges held. I'm not an easy man to get along with, sometimes. Sol knows a lot of people around here have learned that lesson...

g.title: j653284605
g.text: Mmm, I'm keeping my options open.

g.title: j739414966
g.text: All right then. I'm going to go off and have a serious think.

g.title: j36672327
g.text: I'm just not the easily sharing type. But maybe well get there, someday.

g.title: j3720510151
g.text: Heh. Good to know. Something to look forward to.

g.title: j1358306500
g.text: Here's a toast to Someday, then.

g.title: j180503250
g.text: Can I ask how you got the skana in the first place?
